##Grants and bursaries

Student loans have to be paid back - grants, bursaries and allowances do not.

<% if eligible_for_nhs_bursary %>
  You can apply for [NHS funding towards your fees and living costs](/nhs-bursaries).
<% elsif course_studied == "teacher-training" %>
  You can apply for [funding for teacher training](/teacher-training-funding).
<% elsif course_studied == "social-work" %>
  You can apply for a [Social Work Bursary](/social-work-bursaries).
<% end %>

You could get a [bursary or scholarship](/extra-money-pay-university) from your university or college.

Use the [Turn2us grant search](http://grants-search.turn2us.org.uk/) to check whether you qualify for funding from a charitable trust.